Afe 1981 mu ɛna Andam bɛyɛɛ kyerɛkyerɛni wɔ Kwame Nkrumah suapɔn mu.  Ɔyɛɛ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ fa a ɛhwɛ mfididwuma ne ahoɔden  akyerɛkyerɛfoɔ panin wɔ suapɔn no mu afe 2000, ɛna ɔyɛɛ ɔtitena nii maa WILKADO wɔ afe 2005.  Ɔka wɔn a wɔyɛ nhwehwɛmu wɔ mfididwuma ne ahoɔden mu wɔ Kumasi Nuclear Research Laboratory. Ɔkyerɛɛ adeɛ kakra wɔ Oguaa suapɔn mu ( University of Cape Coast). Afe 1996-2002 mu no ɔyɛɛ otitena nii maa UNESCO; Women in Science and Technology wɔ abibirem atɔeɛ fam'..
